---
// 섹션 5: 추천 차트 — 좌 통계/우 라인차트
---

<div class="featured-chart">
  <div>
    <div class="fc-meta-label">통 계 · 일 갱 신</div>
    <h3 class="fc-title">원/달러 환율, 6주 만에 1,360원대 회복</h3>
    <p class="fc-desc">
      한국은행 ECOS 일일 종가 기준. 4월 28일 1,387원 고점 이후 5거래일 연속 하락. 5월 FOMC 의사록 발표를 앞두고 외환시장 변동성은 12.4%로 평년 수준.<sup class="fn">[3]</sup>
    </p>
    <div class="fc-stats">
      <div class="fc-stat">
        <div class="fc-stat-label">5월 5일 종가</div>
        <div class="fc-stat-value">1,362.40<span class="unit">원</span></div>
        <div class="fc-stat-delta down">▼ −24.6 (−1.78%)</div>
      </div>
      <div class="fc-stat">
        <div class="fc-stat-label">52주 변동폭</div>
        <div class="fc-stat-value">1,287 — 1,397</div>
        <div class="fc-stat-delta">+8.5% YoY</div>
      </div>
      <div class="fc-stat">
        <div class="fc-stat-label">변동성 (30D)</div>
        <div class="fc-stat-value">12.4<span class="unit">%</span></div>
        <div class="fc-stat-delta down">평년 13.1%</div>
      </div>
      <div class="fc-stat">
        <div class="fc-stat-label">갱신 시각</div>
        <div class="fc-stat-value fc-stat-value-mono">2026-05-05 18:00</div>
        <div class="fc-stat-delta">출처: BOK ECOS</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="fc-chart-frame">
    <div class="fc-chart-head">
      <div class="fc-chart-title-sm">원/달러 환율 (KRW/USD) — 일 종가</div>
      <div class="fc-chart-toggle">
        <button>1M</button>
        <button class="on">3M</button>
        <button>1Y</button>
        <button>5Y</button>
      </div>
    </div>
    <svg class="line-chart" viewBox="0 0 600 240" preserveAspectRatio="none">
      <line x1="0" x2="600" y1="40" y2="40" stroke="#e0ddd0" stroke-width="0.5" stroke-dasharray="2,4" />
      <line x1="0" x2="600" y1="100" y2="100" stroke="#e0ddd0" stroke-width="0.5" stroke-dasharray="2,4" />
      <line x1="0" x2="600" y1="160" y2="160" stroke="#e0ddd0" stroke-width="0.5" stroke-dasharray="2,4" />
      <text x="592" y="44" text-anchor="end" font-family="JetBrains Mono" font-size="9" fill="#a5a5a5">1,400</text>
      <text x="592" y="104" text-anchor="end" font-family="JetBrains Mono" font-size="9" fill="#a5a5a5">1,360</text>
      <text x="592" y="164" text-anchor="end" font-family="JetBrains Mono" font-size="9" fill="#a5a5a5">1,320</text>
      <polyline
        fill="none"
        stroke="#1a1a1a"
        stroke-width="1.4"
        points="0,170 25,165 50,158 75,150 100,145 125,140 150,148 175,135 200,128 225,120 250,108 275,98 300,85 325,72 350,60 375,48 400,42 425,55 450,68 475,82 500,95 525,108 550,118 575,128 600,132"
      />
      <circle cx="600" cy="132" r="3" fill="#8b1538" />
      <text x="588" y="124" text-anchor="end" font-family="JetBrains Mono" font-size="10" fill="#8b1538" font-weight="500">1,362.40</text>
    </svg>
    <div class="fc-chart-foot">
      <span>2026-02-05</span>
      <span>출처: 한국은행 ECOS · 일 종가 기준</span>
      <span>2026-05-05</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .featured-chart {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.5fr;
    gap: 56px;
    align-items: start;
  }
  @media (max-width: 880px) {
    .featured-chart {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 24px;
    }
  }

  .fc-meta-label {
    color: var(--color-ink-tertiary);
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .fc-title {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 26px;
    line-height: 1.3;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    color: var(--color-ink);
    margin: 0 0 14px;
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .fc-desc {
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-ink-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .fc-stats {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 0;
    border-top: 0.5px solid var(--color-ink-quat);
  }
  .fc-stat {
    padding: 12px 0;
    border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--color-ink-quat);
  }
  .fc-stat:nth-child(odd) { padding-right: 16px; }
  .fc-stat:nth-child(even) {
    padding-left: 16px;
    border-left: 0.5px solid var(--color-ink-quat);
  }
  .fc-stat-label {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--color-ink-tertiary);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .fc-stat-value {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    color: var(--color-ink);
  }
  .fc-stat-value.fc-stat-value-mono {
    font-size: 14px;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
  }
  .fc-stat-value .unit {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--color-ink-secondary);
    margin-left: 2px;
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
  }
  .fc-stat-delta {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-top: 2px;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }
  .fc-stat-delta.down {
    color: #1f4d8a;
  }

  .fc-chart-frame {
    border: 0.5px solid var(--color-ink-quat);
    padding: 24px 28px 20px;
  }
  .fc-chart-head {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: baseline;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    padding-bottom: 10px;
    border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--color-ink-quat);
  }
  .fc-chart-title-sm {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--color-ink);
  }
  .fc-chart-toggle {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: var(--color-ink-tertiary);
  }
  .fc-chart-toggle button {
    background: none;
    border: 0;
    font: inherit;
    color: inherit;
    cursor: pointer;
    padding: 0;
  }
  .fc-chart-toggle button.on {
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }
  .line-chart {
    width: 100%;
    height: 240px;
    display: block;
  }
  .fc-chart-foot {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    margin-top: 12px;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--color-ink-tertiary);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }
</style>
